<h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-2 leading-tight">Best Scrabble Dictionary Apps</h1>
<p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-8 not-prose">Bingo · Anagram · Scrabble Words Finder</p>

<p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6">Published June 15, 2026 · 6 min read</p>

<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">A reliable dictionary app is every Scrabble player's best training partner. Whether you need to verify a challenged word, study obscure two-letter gems, or explore anagram possibilities, the right app makes all the difference between casual play and competitive confidence.</p>

<div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 my-8 p-4 rounded-lg border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10">
  <div class="text-center"><span class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">280K+</span><br><span class="text-xs text-gray-400">SOWPODS Words</span></div>
  <div class="text-center"><span class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">187K+</span><br><span class="text-xs text-gray-400">TWL06 Words</span></div>
  <div class="text-center"><span class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">6+</span><br><span class="text-xs text-gray-400">Top Apps Reviewed</span></div>
</div>

<h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Understanding Scrabble Dictionaries</h2>

<p>Before choosing an app, it helps to understand the dictionaries that power them. Tournament Scrabble uses two main word lists, and your app must match the one used in your region or club.</p>

<div class="overflow-x-auto my-6">
<table class="w-full text-sm">
  <thead><tr class="bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800"><th class="p-2 text-left">Dictionary</th><th class="p-2 text-left">Full Name</th><th class="p-2 text-left">Region</th><th class="p-2 text-left">Word Count</th></tr></thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr><td class="p-2">SOWPODS</td><td class="p-2">Collins Scrabble Words (CSW)</td><td class="p-2">International</td><td class="p-2">~280,000</td></tr>
    <tr class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800/50"><td class="p-2">TWL06</td><td class="p-2">Tournament Word List</td><td class="p-2">North America</td><td class="p-2">~187,000</td></tr>
    <tr><td class="p-2">OSPD</td><td class="p-2">Official Scrabble Players Dictionary</td><td class="p-2">Casual (US/CA)</td><td class="p-2">~100,000</td></tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
</div>

<p>SOWPODS includes every word from both TWL and the international Collins list. If a word is valid in TWL, it is always valid in SOWPODS — but not vice versa. This distinction matters when choosing your app's dictionary setting.</p>

<h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Top Dictionary Apps Compared</h2>

<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 my-6">
