<p>Free dictionary apps typically offer basic word validation. Paid versions add features that serious players rely on daily:</p>

<div class="overflow-x-auto my-6">
<table class="w-full text-sm">
  <thead><tr class="bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800"><th class="p-2 text-left">Feature</th><th class="p-2 text-left">Free Apps</th><th class="p-2 text-left">Paid Apps</th></tr></thead>
