    <tr class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800/50"><td class="p-2">Quizzing & study tools</td><td class="p-2">❌</td><td class="p-2">✅</td></tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
</div>

<p>For casual players, free apps are perfectly adequate. If you attend clubs or tournaments, the paid upgrade pays for itself quickly through improved word knowledge and study efficiency.</p>

<h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Choosing the Right App for Your Level</h2>

<p>Your ideal dictionary app depends on where you are in your Scrabble journey. A beginner overwhelmed by 280,000 words needs a different tool than a tournament veteran drilling bingo stems.</p>

<div class="space-y-3 my-6">
  <div class="p-3 rounded border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors">
